2. MENU

After loading the game you will be presented with the main menu.
The choices are:

                                A. START GAME
                                B. LOAD GAME
                                C. CREDITS
                                D. QUIT

2a. START GAME

This will take you to the graduation screen. You will be asked to enter
your name and the name of your ship. Then you will be asked to accept these
details or to change them.
If you accept you will then goto the Federation HQ space station orbiting
Earth. You are now ready to fly.


2b. LOAD GAME

If you have previously saved a game you can load the data and start from
where you left off.


2c. CREDITS

Take a look and see.


2d. QUIT

Takes you back to Workbench.

