4. STARTING UP

Now that you have arrived at the Federation HQ space station, you are ready
to begin. You have $5000 to spend as you want but it probably won't be enough
to buy what you really need.
First of all you will need to buy some fuel from the station market.
Initially you can carry up to 15t of fuel which will be enough to get you to
a few of the nearest star systems. You can also carry up to 15t of cargo.
The cargo bay and the fuel tank can be expanded. These are available at
the stations upgrades section.

After stocking up on fuel, check out the Federation to see what mission
they have for you.
If you think you can handle it, accept the mission. Then goto the Bulletin
Board to see if there are any packages to be delivered to the system you're
heading to or even any systems that are near it.
Use the starmap to plan your route and read the description of the systems.
There are a few clues in the description as to what goes on and the imports/
exports.
For instance, if it is a mining colony then it will be a good chance they
will import machinery. If you have the cash and the space, buy a few tonnes
and take a chance. You never know.

Once your ready, select leave station and prepare for battle.

