7. UPGRADES

Your starship comes with the following equipment:

                                Cargo bay M1
                                Fuel Tank M1
                                Drive Class 1
                                1 Mw Laser 

The following upgrades are available:

                               A. CARGO BAY M2
                               B. CARGO BAY M3
                               C. CARGO BAY M4
                               D. FUEL TANK M2
                               E. FUEL TANK M3
                               F. FUEL TANK M4
                               G. DRIVE CLASS 2
                               H. DRIVE CLASS 3
                               I. MISSILES
                               J. ENERGY BOMB
                               K. 5 Mw LASER
                               L. 10 Mw LASER
                               M. 20 Mw LASER
                               N. 5 Mw BEAM LASER
                               O. 10 Mw BEAM LASER
                               P. 20 Mw BEAM LASER
                               Q. SHEILD BOOSTER


7a. CARGO BAY M2

This will increase your hold capacity to 35t and cost approx $8000.


7b. CARGO BAY M3

This will increase your hold capacity to 70t and cost approx $15000.


7c. CARGO BAY M4

This will increase your hold capacity to 100t and cost approx $25000.


7d. FUEL TANK M2

This will increase your fuel capacity to 20t and cost approx $8000.


7e. FUEL TANK M3

This will increase your fuel capacity to 35t and cost approx $15000.


7f. FUEL TANK M4

This will increase your fuel capacity to 50t and cost approx $25000.


7g. DRIVE CLASS 2

This drive will enable you to travel twice as fast and use about half the
normal amount of fuel. It uses 20t of cargo space and costs approx $15000.


7h. DRIVE CLASS 3

This drive will enable you to travel three times as fast and use about
three times less fuel than normal.
It uses 40t of cargo space and costs approx $30000.


7i. MISSILES

You can carry up to 14 pairs of missiles. Each pair takes up 2t of cargo
space and costs approx $4000.
Any ship hit by a missile will instantly be destroyed.


7j. ENERGY BOMB

You can only have one energy bomb but they are extremely usefull as they
do a lot of damage. They take up 4t of cargo space and cost approx $5000.


7k. 5 Mw LASER

This takes up 5t of cargo space and costs approx $5000.


7l. 10 Mw LASER

This takes up 10t of cargo space and costs approx $8000.


7m. 20 Mw LASER

This takes up 15t of cargo space and costs approx $15000.


7n. 5 Mw BEAM LASER

This takes up 20t of cargo space and costs approx $25000.


7o. 10 Mw BEAM LASER

This takes up 25t of cargo space and costs approx $35000.


7p. 20 Mw BEAM LASER

This takes up 30t of cargo space and costs approx $50000.


7q. SHIELD BOOSTER

You can carry up to three of these. Each booster will increase your shields
by 100%. They use 3t of cargo space each and cost approx $15000.


BUYING & SELLING

If you want to buy an upgrade and you already have an earlier model, you will
have to sell it first. Unless it is the basic model which comes with the
ship.

Also, if you want to sell your cargo bay and have it stocked up with cargo
und other upgrades, you will have to sell a few things.
The same applies to the fuel tank. If you have 30t of fuel you can't sell
it until you sell enough fuel.
It's logical, really it is!

